      <title>Private House sales trend growing in the market struggle</title>
      <link>http://www.propertyflaunt.com/blog/index.php?blog=1&amp;title=private_house_sales_trend_growing_in_the&amp;more=1&amp;c=1&amp;tb=1&amp;pb=1</link>
