      <description>Hey!

Hope you have had a great month.

Well, as the U.K market continues its apparent descent one thing that appears to be growing is the presence of private house sales and peoples acceptance that private home selling is an effective and viable way to sell your home, this acceptance is further re-inforced by the massive savings to be had in terms of estate agents fee's saved.

More and more people have realised that to sell property privately all you need are: 

.Common sense
 
.Decent organisational skills 

.The desire to save a considerable sum of money 

Figures from the Office of Fair Trading show that 1 in 10 homeowners now attempt to sell property privately. 
The OFT interviewed a sample of these private sellers and their findings were dramatic:
 
91% reported the whole process ran extremely smoothly. Most said they would do it again.

Compare that to the findings of the Which? report which stated: 
50% of sellers who used Estate Agents were dissatisfied with the service they received.

There is even a recent study by the "Interactive in Media Retail Group", IMRG (The global e-retailing industry body) looking at the rise in popularity of selling a house privately. 
They forecast that by 2010 nearly half (that's 700,000) of all property sold in the UK each year will be without the help of a traditional Estate Agent. 

With todays market where properties are becoming increasingly harder to sell and competition is even greater people are beginning to try everything in a bid to find a buyer and are suprised to find that although they considered private house sales as a last resort it really does work in giving estate agents a run for their money, and in terms of value for money far eclipses the dated traditional moethod of house selling.

If you would like to save thousands whilst selling your house and moving on with your life sign up with www.propertyflaunt.com to expose your house to millions immediately.What will you spend the thousands on that you will save? A new Car, Holiday, Kithen? Dare to dream because with our cost cutting property solutions you can afford to!

Good Luck In all your Property Persuits!

Until next time.

The Property Flaunt Team
