Prices will indeed fall, reposessions are set to soar and properties will be harder to sell,one thing that we must remember however is that like the seasons the U.K property market is a cycle.Some Winters are longer than others but ultimately the Spring will arrive.There is an American philosopher called Jim Rohn who explains the metaphor of the seasons in such a way we believe it will help you or indeed anyone, in times when your circumstance may not be in the direction you had hoped for. <br />
